      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.classes.tcQlonOTpuaKeGLs]{Evolutionist}</p>\n<p>Your body eagerly accepts new augmentations, even creating some of the components out of your own flesh. You gain one free augmentation of the type associated with your niche, with a level equal to or lower than your level. Each time you gain a level, you can replace this augmentation using the same restrictions.</p>\n<p>In addition, you reduce the cost of augmentations associated with your niche by 10%. This applies only to augmentations whose item levels are no greater than your evolutionist level.</p>\n<p>If you receive a discount on an augmentation from another source (not counting the augmentation evolutionary focus below) you instead increase that discount by 5%.</p>\n<p>Note that regardless of your niche, species grafts (Starfinder Alien Archive 4 140) qualify for the benefits of this ability, as long as theyâ€™re of the type associated with your niche.</p>"
